The ratio I(P_k,2)/I(P_k,1) grows as (2/φ)^k ≈ 1.236^k.

CHARACTERISTIC ROOTS:
  x=1: φ ≈ 1.618, -1/φ ≈ -0.618 (irrational, golden)
