The pattern: I(C_k, 2) = 2^k + (-1)^k
  k odd:  2^k - 1 = Mersenne number
  k even: 2^k + 1 = Fermat-like number

The 7 = 2^3 - 1 = I(C_3, 2) is the FIRST Mersenne prime.

