  63 = 9 × 7 = I(E_2, 2) × I(C_3, 2) = I(E_2 ⊔ C_3, 2)
  63 = 21 × 3 = I(P_4, 2) × I(E_1, 2) = I(P_4 ⊔ vertex, 2)
